headline: Enterprise Products Before Q3 Earnings: Time to Sell or Reassess?
summary: EPD is set to post Q3 results, with earnings expected to rise 3.1% even as revenues dip 9% amid its heavy Permian exposure.

headline: First Horizon Names Sital K. Mody to its Board of Directors
summary: First Horizon Corporation (NYSE: FHN or "First Horizon") today announced the election of Sital K. Mody, 54, as an independent director to the First Horizon Corporation Board of Directors and the First Horizon Bank Board of Directors.
